481
00:34:56,349 --> 00:34:56,908
Bai Jue!

482
00:34:57,309 --> 00:34:57,948
Dewa Agung!

483
00:34:57,958 --> 00:35:02,952
♪Mencari kau dalam berpuluh-puluh
